            Articles</heading><section id="ID_1438412096577_020" name="s1" temporalId="sch2_s1" class="no_header"><num value="1">1.</num><content>Any coin which is, or was formerly at any time, current coin of Hong Kong or elsewhere.
                <sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2000/65">65 of 2000 s.
                    3</ref>)</sourceNote><marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412096577_028" name="s2" temporalId="sch2_s2" class="no_header"><num value="2">2.</num><content>Any article which has been used, or is intended to be used, for medical,
                dental, veterinary, scientific or industrial
                use.<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412096577_036" name="s3" temporalId="sch2_s3" class="no_header"><num value="3">3.</num><content>Any article of gold
                thread.<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412096577_044" name="s4" temporalId="sch2_s4" class="no_header"><num value="4">4.</num><content>Any raw material (including any bar, plate, sheet, foil, wire, strip or tube)
                or bullion.<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412096577_052" name="s5" temporalId="sch2_s5" class="no_header"><num value="5">5.</num><content>Any article or part of an article which is so small or thin as to render the
