                weight.<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></content></section><section id="ID_1438412096577_060" name="s6" temporalId="sch2_s6" class="no_header"><num value="6">6.</num><content>Any article manufactured more than 100 years ago provided that this is so
